HEADWORD: bedaze
<hw>be*daze"</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <def>to cause to be senseless, groggy,
or dizzy; cause to lose ability to respond normally;
desensitize.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> stun, daze.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

